  Bo5-kiu3 Chhui3.
  Eng Hoat nng7 kok e5 tiong-kan keh chit8 e5 hai2-kiap, khoah poeh-chap8-ji7 li2 poaN3. Ti7 1875 ni5, u7 chit8 e5 Eng-kok lang5 mia5 kio3 Ui2-poe3, put-chi2 gau5 siu5 chui2, tui3 Eng-kok siu5 kau3 Hoat-kok, lek8-ke3 ji7-chap8-it tiam2 cheng khah ke chiu7 kau3-te3. I2-cheng5 bo5 lang5 kau3 hiah gau5 siu5, au7--lai5 khiok u7 kui2-na7 lang5 teh oh8 Ui2-poe3 an2-ni choe3, chong2-si7 long2 boe7 seng5-kong. 
  Pak Bi2-chiu u7 chit8 tiau5 toa7 ho5, kio3-choe3 Ni-a-ka-la, chit tiau5 tui3 I2-li7-ou5 thau3 kau3 An-tat8-lou7-ou5, chha-put-to 115 li2 poaN3. Tiong-kan u7 chit8 e5 chhut-mia5 e5 phak8-pou3, koaiN5 160 chhioh, ho5-bin7 put-chi2 oeh8, ho5-toe2 e5 chhia5-bin7 sng3 iau2 toa7, tui3 teng2-bin7 kau3 e7-bin7 iok-liok8 25 li2. Ho5 e5 siang-peng5 koaiN5 soaN kia7-kia7, sou2-i2 chui2 teh lau5 put-chi2 kin2, sou2 khi2 e5 eng2 chhin-chhiuN7 hai2--nih-e5 chit8-iuN7. U7 si5 lau5-chui2 saN chhiong, oe7 phun3 kau3 kui2-na7 chhioh koaiN5. Lang5 khia7 ti7 hoaN7-teng2, khoaN3-liau2 kau3 beh gong7--khi3. Ui2-poe3 oa2-kho3 i gau5 siu5, siuN7 beh sun7 lau5 siu5--loh8-khi3, lai5 tit-tioh8 toa7 mia5-siaN. u7 peng5-iu2 khng3 i kong2, “Chui2 lau5 hiah kiong5, lang5 e5 lat8 tong3 i boe7-tiau5, chhiat-chhiat m7-thang loh8-khi3 siu5.” Ui2-poe3 kong2, “Chhi3-khoaN3, kap i piaN3 chit8 e5 ji7-un7--leh.” Tui3 an2-ni chit siau-sit thoan5-po3 si3-hng. Kau3 si5, u7 kui2-na7 ban7 lang5, lai5 tiam3 ho5 e5 siang peng5 hoaN7, beh khoaN3 Ui2-poe3 tian2 pun2-su7. Ui2-poe3 tng cheng3-lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 thng3 saN, thiau3-loh8 chui2, khoaN3-kiN3 i thau5-khak phu5-chhut chui2-bin7 chit8 pai2, tu2-tu2 teh hian2-chhut pun2-leng2. Bo5 phah-sng3 chui2 e5 lat8 siuN-kiong5, lang5 tong3-boe7-tiau5, tong7 ke3-lai5, tong7 ke3-khi3, chit8 te3 chioh8 tong7 ke3 chit8 te3 chioh8, chhin-chhiuN7 chha5-phe3 phu5-lai5 phu5-khi3 bo5 tiaN7 bo5 tioh8. Cheng3 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 chit-e5 cheng5-keng2, long2-chong2 gang7-gang7, bo5 hoat-tou7 thang kiu3--i. Ui2-poe3 si2 ti7 toa7 lau5-chui2 e5 tiong-kan. 
  Li7-khui Ui2-poe3 tim5-loh8 chui2 si2 e5 sou2-chai7 bo5 loa7 hng7, ho5--nih8 u7 chit8 e5 chioh8-chhui3, pun2-toe7 lang5 kio3-choe3 “Bo5-kiu3 Chhui3,” i3-su3 si7 kong2, chhui3 e5 teng2-si3 lau5-chui2 khah ban7, lang5 poah8-loh8 iau2-ku2 u7 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 ki-hoe7. Ke3 chit-e5 chhui3, chui2-se3 thai3 kin2, lang5 tim5--loh8, hoaN7-teng2 sui u7 kang2 chheng-ban7 lang5, iah8 si7 gang7-gang7 khoaN3 i si2 na7-tiaN7. Chit-e5 chioh8-chhui3 khiok bo5 loa7 toa7, peng5-siong5 lang5 long2 bo5 soe3-ji7. Chit-e5 chhui3 sit8-chai7 si7 siN-si2 e5 kai3-han7, ti7 chhui3 e5 teng2-si3 iau2-ku2 u7 siN3-mia7 e5 ng3-bang7, kau3 e7-si3 tek-khak tim5 si2. 
  Cha2-jit8 Khong2-chu2 bat kong2, “Lang5 e5 siN3-mia7 chhin-chhiuN7 ho5-chui2 tit8-tit8 lau5--loh8-khi3, jit8-mi5 bo5 soah.” Tioh8 chai lan2 siN3-mia7 iah8 u7 bo5-kiu3 chhui3, iau2-be7 kau3 chhui3, iau2-ku2 u7 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 ki-hoe7, chit8 e7 ke3 chhui3, chiu7 bo5 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 ng3-bang7. Chit-e5 chhui3, lang5 long2 bo5 koan-sim, in-ui7 lang5 peng5-an ke3 jit8, ti7 bo5 phah bo5 sng3 e5 si5 chiu7 ke3--khi3. Sou2-i2 lan2 eng-kai si5-si5 khek-khek soe3-ji7 tiuN-ti5. 
  ChhiaN2 mng7 khoaN3 chheh e5 peng5-iu2, siat-su2 li2 u7 chhin-chhek peng5-iu2 ke3-si3, li2 teh sang3 chong3 e5 si5, kiam2 bo5 siuN7, lang5 e5 siN-si2 bo5 tiaN7-tioh8, liong5-sim khoaN3-kiN3 hit-e5 cheng5-keng2, kiam2 bo5 siu7 kam2-chhiok? Kiam2-chhai2 li2 ngou2-jian5 tu2-tioh8 gui5-hiam2, hiam2-hiam2 si2, ti7 kiaN-hiaN5 e5 si5, liong5-sim tek-khak hoat-hian7. Koh, kiam2-chhai2 li2 tu2-tioh8 phoa3-piN7, ki3-tit pat8 lang5 tu2-tioh8 chit ho7 piN7 si2--e5 chin choe7, chai7 li2 siuN7, taN li2 tu2--tioh8, tek-khak bo5 ng3-bang7 u7 siN3-mia7. Kai-chai3 ti7 bo5 phah-sng3 e5 si5, li2 sou2 chiah8 e5 ioh8 u7 eng3-hau7, piN7-se3 chiam7-chiam7 ho2, li2 e5 siN3-mia7 chhin-chhiuN7 koh khioh--tioh8, chit si5 li2 e5 thian-liong5, iah8 tek-khak hoat-hian7. Li2 ki3-jian5 tit-tioh8 thiN e5 un-tian2, kiam2 m7 si7 Siong7-te3 keng2-seng2--li2--mah? Li2 iu5-goan5 be7 bat sin3-hok8 Kiu3 Chu2, m7 kheng2 khiam-hu sim seng5-siu7 ka3-si7, kiam2 bo5 siuN7 teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2 tak8 hang7, iah8 thang choe3 li2 e5 bo5-kiu3 chhui3--mah? Siong7-te3 kong2, “Goa2 e5 Sin5, tek-khak bo5 eng2-oan2 kap lang5 saN-chiN.” Koh kong2, “Li2 m7-thang phah-biat8 Seng3 Sin5 e5 kam2-tong7.” 
  Chu2 Ki-tok kong2, “Siat-su2 lin2 ti7 kin-a2-jit8, chai koan-he7 ti7 lin2 peng5-an e5 tai7-chi3 chiu7 put-chi2 ho2, chong2 si7 hian7-kim un2-bat8 ti7 lin2 e5 bak8-chiu.” 
  Tit-tioh8 Kiu3 e5 Phio3-ku3. 
  U7 chit8 pai2 goa2 che7 he2-chhia mi5--si5 khui. Kau3 poaN3-mi5 e5 si5, koan2-chhia e5 lang5 kio3 goa2 cheng-sin5, kong2, beh giam7 chhia-phio3. Goa2 theh8 phio3 hou7--i, i khoaN3-khoaN3 chiu7 khi3. Chit hang7 hou7 goa2 e5 sim u7 siu7 kam2-chhiok, in-ui7 koan2-chhia e5 lang5, bo5 chu-chu siong3 lang5 e5 bin7-mau7 siN choe3 siaN2 khoan2, su-bun5 a2-si7 chhou-lou2, hu3-kui3 a2-si7 pin5-chian7, chiah-e5 i long2 bo5 chu3-i3, tok8-tok8 khoaN3 chhia-phio3 u7 chho3 a2 bo5 na7-tiaN7. Tui3 chit hang7 hou7 goa2 siuN7 kiaN5 thiN-lou7 khi3 Thian-tong5 iah8 si7 an2-ni, Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 kong-lo5 chiu7-si7 lan2 e5 phio3-ku3, kau3 sim2-phoaN3 e5 si5, Siong7-te3 bo5 kau3-kham3 lan2 si7 siong7-teng2 lang5 a2-si7 ha7-teng2 lang5. Siong7-te3 tok8-tok8 chha5 lan2 e5 phio3-ku3 tioh8 a2-si7 m7 tioh8 na7-tiaN7. Sou2-i2 lan2 long2 boe7 kong2 tit goa2 si7 kho3 ka-ki7 e5 kong-tek, in-ui7 lan2 e5 kong-tek boe7 sng3 choe3 phio3-ku3, tioh8 kiu5 Chu2 bo5 khoaN3 lan2 e5 kiaN5 choe3, si7 khoaN3 Ki-tok e5 kim-bin7 choe3 lan2 e5 phio3-ku3. 
  Koh bat thiaN-kiN3 kau3-iu2 kong2, “Goa2 boe7 kham-tit jip8 Thian-tong5.” Chit-e5 oe7 khiok iah8 tioh8, in-ui7 se3-kan bo5 chit8 lang5 oe7 kham-tit jip8 Thian-tong5. Siat-su2 hou7 li2 oah8 kau3 chit8-pah-he3, chin7-lat8 siu-heng7 kiaN5 ho2, iu5-goan5 boe7 kham-tit jip8. Siong7-te3 keng2 li2, beh kiu3--li2, m7 si7 in-ui7 li2 eng-kai tit-tioh8 kiu3, chiu7-si7 ui7-tioh8 Ia5-sou thoe3 li2 siu7 chheng-poaN e5 kan-khou2, thoe3 li2 si2 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3 lip8 kong-lo5. Li2 tioh8 chai Ia5-sou e5 kong-lo5 kau3 loa7 toa7 tui3-tiong7. Siong7-te3 khoaN3 chit-e5 kong-lo5 kek8-ki5 po2-poe3, lan2 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 ian5-kou3, chiu7-si7 tui3 Siong7-te3 khoaN3 chit-e5 po2-poe3 e5 kong-lo5, sou2-i2 siuN7 jip8 Thian-tong5 e5 lang5, bian2 giau5-gi5, tok8-tok8 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3 ka-ki7 e5 choe7-ok, sin3-kho3 Ia5-sou e5 kong-lo5, chiu7 oe7 jip8. 
  Pau Soe2 La5-sam5. 
  U7 chit8 jit8, goa2 thau3-cha2 chhut mng5-khau2 tah chit8 tiuN ko3-peh8, kong2, U7 te7 it ho2 eng7 e5 ioh8-liau7, bo5 lun7 i-chiuN5 u7 sim2-mih8 la5-sam5, eng7 chit ho7 ioh8 chit8 e7 chhit, bo5 m7 chheng-khi3 chhin-chhiuN7 sin.” Moa2 tiuN kong2 kau3 chiah nih8 ho2, hiah nih8 ho2, ai3 lang5 boe2 lai5 chhi3 eng7. 
  Goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 ko3-peh8, chiu7 siuN7 i-chiuN5 la5-sam5, lang5-lang5 long2 khoaN3--kiN3, chai ka-ki7 kap lang5 bo5 chhin-chhiuN7, siuN7 liau2 chin kian3-siau3, sou2-i2 tek-khak siat-hoat hou7 i chheng-khi3. Se3-kan lang5 sim-lai7 e5 la5-sam5, ka-ki7 chai, Siong7-te3 khoaN3--kiN3, hoan2-tng2 bo5 liah8 choe3 kian3-siau3, soa3 eng7 ban7 hang7 e5 ke3-bou5, siuN7 beh jia-iam2 hou7 lang5 m7 chai, na7 jia-iam2 tit ho2, long2 bo5 pit-phang7, chiu7 ho7 choe3 oan5-choan5 chheng-khi3-siuN3 e5 lang5. M7 ku2 jim7 li2 jia-iam2, iah8 jia-iam2 boe7-bat8, cha2-oaN3 chong2 u7 chhut-phoa3 e5 si5, kau3 hit si5 tek-khak moa5 boe7 ke3. Siat-su2 chit8-si3-lang5 ng kau3 bat8-bat8, beh si2 e5 si5, bo5 phai3-phe e5 tiong-kan kong2--chhut-lai5. In-ui7 kou2-cha2 lang5 kong2, “Lang5 kau3 beh si2 e5 si5, i sou2 kong2 e5 oe7 ho2.” Koh hit si5 thian-liong5 hoat-hian7, ka-ki7 chai sin-khu li7-khui se3-kan, leng5-hun5 tioh8 khia7 ti7 Siong7-te3 sim2-phoaN3 e5 tai5-cheng5, hou7 I sim2-phoaN3, chit8-si3-lang5 e5 choe7-ok, bo5 chit8 si bo5 hian2-beng5. Kau3 chit tiap8 chiah beh hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3, i2-keng oaN3--lah. Na7 oe7 ti7 siN-cheng5 u7 hoat-tou7, chiong sim-lai7 e5 choe7-ok la5-sam5 soe2 chheng, kiam2 bo5 chin ho2. Chong2-si7 chit hang7 lang5-lang5 chai si7 oh e5 su7. Siok8-gu2 kong2, “Jim7 li2 iuN2 chin7 Se-kang chui2, iah8 oh soe2-khi3 moa2 bin7 siu.” Che si7 piau2-beng5 oh soe2 choe7 e5 pin5-ku3. Goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 ko3-peh8, chiu7 siuN7 na7 lang5 u7 ioh8 oe7 soe2 lang5 sim-lai7 choe7-ok e5 la5-sam5, boe7 ioh8--e5 tek-khak toa7 hoat-chai5, in-ui7 thiN-e7 tak8 lang5 sim-lai7 u7 la5-sam5, lang5-lang5 ai3 beh tu5, thang bian2 siN-cheng5 si2-au7 e5 po3-eng3. 
  Seng3-keng kong2, “U7 soe2 chheng choe7-ok e5 ioh8, beh peh8-peh8 hou7--lang5, khang-chhiu2 chin3-cheng5, chiu7 u7 thang tit-tioh8 chit-e5 un-tian2.” Chit ho7 ioh8 chiu7-si7 Seng3-keng sou2 kong2, “Lan2 na7 ti7 kng-beng5 e5 tiong-kan kiaN5, Sin5 e5 KiaN2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 huih, soe2 chheng lan2 long2-chong2 e5 choe7.” ChhiaN2 mng7 khoaN3 chheh e5 lang5, li2 kaN2 kong2 li2 e5 sim-lai7, chheng-khi3 peh8-peh8 chhin-chhiuN7 seh a2-bo5? Khe2-si7-liok8 1:5, kong2, “ThiaN3--lan2-e5, eng7 I e5 huih hou7 lan2 thoat-li7 choe7-koa3.” 
  Siong7-te3 Theng3-hau7--Li2. 
  U7 chit8 e5 siau3-lian5 lang5, sim tit-tioh8 Seng3 Sin5 kam2-tong7, siong5-siong5 kiaN-kiaN hiaN5-hiaN5, chai ka-ki7 si7 choe7-jin5, hoan5-lo2 Siong7-te3 e5 siu7-khi3 lim5-kau3, boe7 thang siam2-pi7. Chiu7 khi3 chhe7 chit8 e5 peng5-iu2, kiu5 i chi2-si7 soe2 choe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 hoat-tou7. Peng5-iu2 kong2, “Li2 oe7 hiau2 chai choe7 lai5 khoa3-sim, che-chiu7 si7 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3 e5 thau5 chit8 pou7, kau3 ti7 tit-tioh8 kiu3, tioh8 theng3-hau7 chu2 ho2 e5 si5-ki5,” Siau3-lian5 lang5 kong2, “goa2 tioh8 theng3-hau7 loa7 ku2?” Peng5-iu2 kong2, “chiah-e5 m7 si7 goa2 sou2 oe7 chai, iah8 m7 si7 goa2 sou2 kaN2 koat-toan3, tok8-tok8 thun-lun2 theng3-hau7 Chu2 e5 un kang3-lim5 na7-tiaN7.” Tui3 an2-ni siau3-lian5 lang5 thun-lun2 theng3-hau7, na2 theng3-hau7, sim na2 bo5 peng5-an. Koh khi3 chhe7 chit8 e5 peng5-iu2, eng7 sim-lai7 sou2 kan-khou2 e5 ka7 i kong2. Peng5-iu2 kong2, “li2 na7 pek-chhiat ki5-to2, chu7-jian5 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 un.” siau3-lian5 kong2, “Goa2 tioh8 ki5-to2 kau3 sim2-mih8 si5?” Peng5-iu2 kong2, “Siong5-siong5 ki5-to2 bo5 soah, kau3 be2 tek-khak u7 chit8 jit8 oe7 tit-tioh8 un-tian2.”Siau3-lian5 lang5 than3 i e5 oe7, ki5-to2 saN ni5 bo5 lang3, sim-lai7 e5 kan-khou2 iah8 bo5 khah khin. Chiu7 giau5-gi5 nng7 e5 peng5-iu2 e5 oe7 boe7 sin3--tit, koh khi3 chhe7 chit8 e5 peng5-iu2 tui3 i chheng2-kau3, soa3 chiong teng2-bin7 nng7 e5 peng5-iu2 e5 oe7, kap pun2-sin sou2 keng-ke3 e5 cheng5-heng5 ka7 i kong2. Peng5-iu2 kong2, “Li2 chho3--lah, Siong7-te3 ku2-ku2 teh theng3-hau7--li2, mih-sai2 hou7 li2 theng3-hau7. Siong7-te3 cha2-cha2 chhe I e5 KiaN2 Ki-tok Ia5-sou, thoe3 li2 si2 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3, si7 teh theng3-hau7 li2 sin3, kui-oa2, piaN3 sim lai5 seng5-siu7 un-tian2.” Siau3-lian5 lang5 thiaN liau2, chhin-chhiuN7 hun5-bu7 khui jit8-thau5 chhut, sim toa7 hiau2-gou7, chit si5 i2-au7 seng5-sim kui Chu2, sim-koaN put-chi2 peng5-an. 
  Ki-tok kong2, “Hoan7-na7 tioh8-boa5, kan-khou2, pe7 tang7-taN3 e5 lang5 chiu7-kun7 goa2, goa2 siuN2-su3 li2 peng5-an.” (Ma2-thai3 11:18[28].) 
  Lip8-chi3. 
  Ai3 choe3 seng3-tou5, thau5 chit8 hang7 tioh8 lip8-chi3, chhi3 cheng7-cheng7 che7 ka-ki7 siuN7, chin-chiaN3 u7 tit-tioh8 kiu3 a2-bo5? Chit-e5 iau3-kin2 e5 mng7-toe5, kap ka-ki7 e5 siN3-mia7 u7 koan-he7, pat8 lang5 tek-khak boe7 thang ka7 li2 tau3 phah-sng3; chong2-si7 chi3 i2-keng koat-toan3, chiu7 tioh8 soa3 sit8-heng5. Pi2-pheng7 u7 lang5 tiaN7-tioh8 beh khi3 kiaN-siaN5, chong2-si7 chi3 sui-jian5 lip8, m7-ku2 sin-khu m7 kiaN5, chiu7 boe7 chiah8 boe7 khun3 lai5 siuN7, iah8 si7 bo5 li7-ek, tek-khak tioh8 pi7-pan7 sou2-hui3, khoan2 heng5-li2, thiah chun5-toaN, boe2 chhia-phio3 khi2-sin, chiah oe7 kau3 sou2 ai3 kau3 e5 sou2-chai7. Lan2 ai3 choe3 Ki-tok chin e5 hak8-seng, khun5-khun5 hok8-sai7 Chu2, tak8 sou2-chai7 khak-sit8 siu2 Seng3 e5 ka3-si7. Ti7 pun2-sin tioh8 choe3, pat8 lang5 bo5 kan-siap8. 
  Cha2-jit8 A-pek-liap8-han2 ka7 kiaN2 chhoa7 sim-pu7 Li7-pek-ka, chhe lou5-pok8 khi3 ngia5-chih. Li7-pek-ka e5 pe7-bu2, chhin-chhek, lau5 Li7-pek-ka, boe7 jim2-tit liam5-piN hou7 i khi3, lou5-pok8 kong2, “I2-keng kiat-iok choe3 chhin, na7 koh-chai3 lau5, kiaN-liau2 hou7 goa2 e5 chu2-lang5 toa7 siau3-liam7.” U7 e5 kong2, “Che si7 sin-niu5 e5 tai7-chi3, tioh8 hou7 I ka-ki7 chu2-i3.” Cheng3-lang5 long2 chan3-seng5, chiu7 kio3 Li7-pek-ka lai5 mng7, kong2, “Li2 hoaN-hi2 liam5-piN te3 lau7 lou5-pok8 khi3--mah?”In3 kong2, “Ho2.” Chiu7 saN-kap khi2-sin. Chit-e5 chiu7-si7 lip8-chi3 e5 bou5-iuN7. Koh Lou7-tek iu2-hau3 hok8-sai7 ta-ke, tiong7-hu si2, ta-ke kio3 i to3-tng2 khi3 goa7-ke chhu3. Lou7-tek m7 kheng2, in-ui7 to3-khi3 tioh8 hok8-sai7 ngou2-siong7, iu7 boe7 thang te3 ta-ke, kau3 Siong7-te3 siuN2-su3 hok-khi3 e5 sou2-chai7. Kiu5 ta-ke kong2, “Li2 m7-thang pek goa2 to3--khi3, li2 khi3 e5 sou2-chai7, goa2 iah8 beh kau3 hia, li2 sou2 pai3 e5 Siong7-te3, iah8 chiu7-si7 goa2 e5 Siong7-te3.” Chiu7 bo5 to3-khi3 goa7-ke tau. (Lou7-tek-ki3 1:16, 17.) chit-e5 iah8 si7 lip8-chi3 u7 sit8-sit8 kiaN5 e5 chit8 hang7 pin5-ku3. 
  Lip8-chi3 Hok8-sai7 Chu2 e5 Lang5 e5 Ki5-to2-bun5. 
  Goa2 e5 Kiu3 Chu2 ah, Li2 lau5 huih lai5 soe2 goa2 e5 choe7, pang3-sak sin-khu lai5 siok8 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5, goa2 m7 chai thang than3 Li2 e5 beng7-leng7, hap8 Li2 Seng3 e5 sim, un-tian2 jin5-chu5 moa2-moa2 thiN-toe7 lai7, goa2 khi2-thau5 bo5 seng2-chhat. Kau3 taN chiah chai, toa7-toa7 siu7 tioh8 kam2-kek, tok8-tok8 eng7 goa2 e5 sin-khu leng5-hun5, in-ui7 Kiu3 Chu2 lai5 hian3 hou7 ThiN-pe7. Tui3 taN liau2-au7 beh soe3-ji7 than3 Chu2 e5 to7-li2 kau3 chit8-si3-lang5 bo5 pian3-oaN7. Sim sou2 goan7. 
